---
globs: **/*.vue, **/composables/*.ts
alwaysApply: false
---

API style:
- Use exclusively Composition API with `<script setup lang="ts">`
- Never use Options API (`data()`, `methods:`, `computed:` as object properties, `this`)
- Never use `defineComponent()` with an options object
- Never use mixins; replace with composables (`use*` functions in `composables/`)

Script setup:
- Always declare `lang="ts"` on the `<script setup>` block
- Vue APIs (`ref`, `computed`, `watch`, lifecycle hooks) are imported directly or auto-imported by Nuxt
- Top-level variables, functions, and imports in `<script setup>` are automatically available in the template
